people are doing-- turning off

00:56:17.470 --> 00:56:21.590 align:middle line:84%
the TV, et cetera, is it
good for us in general

00:56:21.590 --> 00:56:24.135 align:middle line:84%
to start doing the TRE exercises
together or alone even?

00:56:24.135 --> 00:56:26.010 align:middle line:84%
>>BERCELI: I think it's
