is because if it's still

00:56:28.860 --> 00:56:30.780 align:middle line:84%
built into our
nervous system, then

00:56:30.780 --> 00:56:32.950 align:middle line:84%
as part of our
evolutionary process,

00:56:32.950 --> 00:56:34.590 align:middle line:84%
our nervous system
must still think we

00:56:34.590 --> 00:56:36.570 align:middle line:90%
need that to actually survive.

00:56:36.570 --> 00:56:38.720 align:middle line:10%
So I think every
human person, just

